1/installed bootstrap
npm install --save-dev bootstrap
2/
Then you can remove from the html file, the import statement for bootstrap

3/ change the .css file to .scss
4/ load the sass loader:
https://webpack.js.org/loaders/sass-loader/

5/ add to webpack input file (index.js in our case)
import "./main.scss";

6/ import bootstram in the main.scss file:
@import "~bootstrap/scss/bootstrap";
